This Type C to Type C Charger Cord has been certified to various standards, no need to worry about the quality of this cord, which is a perfect replacement for the original official cable.

SOFT & DURABLE - The Fast Charger USB C Cord has a soft surface made of high quality TPE material for safety and durability. This USBC charger has a soft feel and flexes well that will bounce back after sitting bent. Its excellent flexibility allows it to be tucked into a bag or pocket without tangling. UNIVERSAL COMPATIBILITY - The reversible USB C Fast Charger Cable has a USB Type C connector on each end, and can easily connects all USB-C enabled devices, no matter which side is up. The USBC cable works with iOS devices, Android devices and more, perfectly compatible with i Phone 15/15 Pro/15 Pro Max/15 Plus, i Pad Pro 2021/2020/2019/2018, iPad Air 4, i Pad mini 6, MacBook Pro 13/14/15/16 inch, Samsung Galaxy S23 S23+ S23 Ultra S22 S21 S20 S10, Pixel 7 Pro, and any other USB-C devices.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 6, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Cute colors for nice, sturdy charging cables!
reviews.reviewText: I needed USB-C to USB-C cables in this nice 6 foot length and was happy to find a pair in pretty colors! Hey, if you gotta do something boring like charge your Ipad/Iphone you might as well have some color lol! This length is perfect; the 3 footers are just uselessly short, and 10 foot is just too long with too much extra cord to deal with unless you are really far from that outlet! The silicon coating on these cables feels nice, and the cables seem sturdy enough to me. The silicon around the ends does seem like it would help them bend and hold up longer than older cables I have had. No way to know this for sure, but I will update review if they don’t hold up. The ends go in my Ipad and my fast charging puck very smoothly. The price is pretty decent for USB-C to USB-c and considering the pretty colors. The colors also would be nice to differentiate which cable goes to which device or person. All is all, a good buy! (I do agree with other reviewer that a pair of matching color fast-charging USB-C pucks would have been nice!)

reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Actually fast charges
reviews.reviewText: I have gotten a handful of cords that promise they are fast charging and they never work even with our plug that is a fast charger. These actually fast charge. The colors are nice, the extra length it nice and they actually work as promised.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 16, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Bought it for the two colors!
reviews.reviewText: I selected these cables because of the two colors, pink and lavender. Charging cables are functional tools so it's ncie when they come in beautiful colors. You can always distinguish your own cables because of the bright colors.I picked six feet in lengh because It is not too short or too long. The silicon cord appears to be flexible and I was able to use one of them to charge my Samsung S22 phone with same fast speed as the original cable.I hope they include charger plugs in matching pink and lavender next time.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 6, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars Pretty and durable USB-C charging cables
reviews.reviewText: These charging cables are a very pretty pink and lavender, which I love! They are made with silicone, which is a first for me with charging cables, and they flex nicely and can bend to fit your charging and storage needs without denting. Length is long and convenient for charging options. I do wish that there was an option to have bricks included (especially in the same colors!), as unless you plan to charge with a computer that has a USB-C port, you will need a brick with a USB-C connector to plug into an outlet, so I had to find and buy that separately (not in matching colors).

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 18, 2024
reviews.reviewText: Only time will tell, but these seem sturdy and like they will last. I plugged my Kindle into my laptop to charge, and they seem to work. It plugged easily into my Kindle, but was a bit more difficult to get plugged into the laptop USB-C. I really like the colors, as pink is my favorite color and purple is close behind. They are pretty shades, and so much nicer than boring white or black!

reviews.reviewText: I got this for my daughter for her macbook. She is using this in place of the original apple USB type C charging cable. It looks vibrant, and it charges her macbook without any issues.
